clash in the border area in at least 45 years.

12
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:53,110
Chinese and Indian soldiers had engaged in
hand to hand combat, in the dark, on dangerous

13
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:55,120
mountain slopes.

14
00:00:55,120 --> 00:01:01,300
