45
00:03:26,459 --> 00:03:30,180
“Of course the highest ranked official stays
alive.

46
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:34,900
I bet he’s got a ‘runaway’ personality.

47
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:39,989
And of course, ‘the Indian troops held their
heads and ran away from us.’

48
00:03:39,989 --> 00:03:41,739
Anyway, we won.”

49
00:03:41,739 --> 00:03:43,739
“Think about it like this.

50
00:03:43,739 --> 00:03:49,830
If the government says these 4 soldiers died
trying to ‘rescue’ other soldiers, then

51
00:03:49,830 --> 00:03:53,500
