rescued.

52
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:57,400
There’s definitely more casualties than
reported.

53
00:03:57,400 --> 00:04:02,890
This makes me understand why India was so
fast to report their casualties, because in

54
00:04:02,890 --> 00:04:08,870
