were less than China’s.”

55
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:14,549
It’s hard to know whether Spicy Pen Ball
is correct.

56
00:04:14,549 --> 00:04:16,410
But one thing’s for sure.

57
00:04:16,410 --> 00:04:20,030
His comments were politically incorrect.

58
00:04:20,030 --> 00:04:46,199
And by the end of the day, the Weibo platform
itself posted this announcement.

59
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:52,240
Which is weird, because he didn’t actually
mention the names of the fallen soldiers,

60
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:55,100
or actually slander them.

61
00:04:55,100 --> 00:05:01,009
But if you think blocking the account for
a year is too harsh, you’re wrong.

62
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:06,960
Because a few hours later, the Weibo platform
posted this update, saying that “According

63
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:16,080
