68
00:05:33,450 --> 00:05:37,290
Qiu Ziming left our company in 2015.

69
00:05:37,290 --> 00:05:40,850
His opinions are not affiliated with our company.

70
00:05:40,850 --> 00:05:47,820
The staff at The Economic Observer are very
respectful and mournful over the sacrifices

71
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:53,330
of our country’s heroes, and we condemn
any slandering on their behalf!”

72
00:05:53,330 --> 00:06:00,750
Yes, Qiu’s post was so influential that
the company he worked at six years ago had

73
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:04,680
to come out and deny any affiliation with
him.

74
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:10,110
The next day, the Nanjing police issued a
notice declaring that they had taken action

75
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:13,169
on this serious, serious issue.

76
00:06:13,169 --> 00:06:22,030
It says, “On the night of February 19, police
captured the perpetrator Spicy Pen Ball.

77
00:06:22,030 --> 00:06:29,590
Spicy Pen Ball has confessed to his ill intention
of seeking attention by bending the truth...

78
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:35,449
The Nanjing Police have placed Spicy Pen Ball
in criminal detention under suspicion of the

79
00:06:35,449 --> 00:06:40,840
crime of picking quarrels and provoking trouble.

80
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,620
Slandering heroes is intolerable.

81
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:47,000
The internet is not outside of the law.

82
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:54,370
The Public Security Bureau will severely punish
those who distort, defame, or deny the heroism

83
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:56,120
of our soldiers.\h

84
00:06:56,120 --> 00:07:02,940
We hope all internet users understand and
follow this law, and help build a healthier

85
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:05,639
and friendly internet community.”

86
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:11,650
Yes, nothing creates a healthy and friendly
community like arresting everyone who commits

87
00:07:11,650 --> 00:07:13,790
thoughtcrime.

88
00:07:13,790 --> 00:07:16,990
And Spicy Pen Ball’s situation is not unique.

89
00:07:16,990 --> 00:07:23,069
Local police bureaus across China have made
similar posts, saying they’ve arrested netizens

90
00:07:23,069 --> 00:07:28,880
who have quote-unquote slandered the names
of the nations’ heroes.

91
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:32,460
Even Chinese people living overseas aren’t
safe.

92
